Wolf of the Aegis Wolves was using his rogue skills to<br>
stealthily conceal himself while waiting for his gruop<br>
to reform.  During that time, a fellow Wolf came under<br>
attack.  Rather than remain secluded, Casben lept from<br>
his cover and rushed to the aid of his packmate and<br>
into an encounter which ultimately resulted in his<br>
death.<br>
<br>
For noble and valorous action to come to the aide of a<br>
packmate in distress which endangered his own life,<br>
the Elders of the Aegis Wolves award Casben the Golden<br>
Aegis.<br>
<br>
Casben is the first recipient of this award on any<br>
server.  Congradulations Casben.<br>
<br>
If you get a chance send Casben a tell congratulating him on the honor he has earned.<br>
<br>
Take care<br>
